    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Printing surfaces, usually rectangular in shape and made of wood, used to print designs onto wallpaper. The surface is first engraved with the design, covered with ink, and then pressed into the printing surface.</Note_Text>
